     m_sTextData "We are a insurgent cell that have been tasked to defend the Alami Sharika mine. Recently a warlord by the name of Waseem Ayman Daoud Emad has hired ION to capture the mine for himself. We need to protect the mine and the loyal workers from the incoming assault."\
     ""
